d CEO). Director of Operations has opened 100+ locations across Chipotle, Taco Bell, Popeyes.","story":"Chefless nutrition concept built for the GLP-1 era \u2014 no bread, no deep fryers, no hoods. 1,000-1,500 sq ft footprint. Pre-programmed ovens. Whole30-approved menu. Engineered for the 38M+ Americans with diabetes + tens of millions on GLP-1 medications. Described as 'easiest concept to operate' by DOO with 100+ location experience.","traction":"Early-stage but structurally aligned with massive demographic shift (GLP-1 medications, metabolic health awareness). Strong operational DNA.","funding":"Seed \u2192 franchise","entry_path":"Founding franchisee / multi-unit developer \u2014 get in at the ground floor with significant territory rights. Capital-light buildout.","dan_value_add":"Capital + brand building + multi-unit franchisee structuring. The GLP-1 thesis is structurally sound.","first_diligence":"Only 3 locations \u2014 is the concept proven at scale? What are actual unit economics? GLP-1 trend is real but is a food franchise the way to play it?","sources":["https://franchise.eatbreadless.com/blog/emerging-health-wellness-franchises-2026/"],"last_updated":"2026-07-18","added_date":"2026-07-18","source_file":"fresh_research"},{"id":"negranti-creamery","name":"Negranti Creamery","category":"Food & Beverage","subcategory":"Sheep milk ice cream / artisan creamery","units":3,"units_text":"3 scoop shops in SLO County, CA (Paso Robles, Atascadero, Tin City)","hq_city":"Paso Robles","hq_state":"CA","lat":35.63,"lng":-120.69,"founded":2010,"status":"target","team":"Alexis Negranti (founder, Cal Poly SLO grad 2009); new owner Jenn N. purchased the business. 500+ East Friesian/Lacaune sheep at Dallas, OR farm.","story":"America's only sheep milk ice cream creamery. Founded by Alexis Negranti in 2010 after graduating from Cal Poly SLO. Vertically integrated \u2014 owns the sheep flock (500+ East Friesian/Lacaune) at a production farm in Dallas, Oregon. Three retail scoop shops in San Luis Obispo County. The sheep milk angle is a genuine moat: higher protein, naturally lower lactose, rich texture. Impossible to replicate quickly because you need the dairy animals.","traction":"3 scoop shops operating across Paso Robles, Atascadero, and Tin City. Active Yelp following with updated 2026 info. Wholesale pints distributed regionally. Press coverage from San Luis Obispo Tribune and SLO CAL tourism.","funding":"Bootstrap","entry_path":"Partner with current owner to fund multi-unit retail expansion beyond SLO County, or invest in wholesale/CPG distribution channel. The farm-to-scoop vertical integration is rare and defensible.","dan_value_add":"Capital for retail expansion + brand building + CPG distribution strategy for pint sales","first_diligence":"Why did Alexis sell, and how committed is the new owner to scaling vs. maintaining boutique scale? Is sheep milk production the bottleneck (seasonal lambing cycle, limited milk yield per ewe vs. cows)?","sources":["https://www.negranticreamery.com/ourstory","https://www.sanluisobispo.com/living/food-drink/article253147313.html","https://www.slocal.com/blog/post/slo-cal-crafters-negranti-creamery/","https://www.yelp.com/biz/negranti-creamery-paso-robles-3"],"buzz_signals":"Only sheep milk ice cream in the US; artisan creamery with own flock; SLO County cult following","last_updated":"2026-07-19","added_date":"2026-07-19","source_file":"discovery_cron"},{"id":"vanguard-key-clubs","name":"Vanguard Key Clubs","category":"Boutique Fitness","subcategory":"24-hour key club gym / value fitness","units":6,"units_text":"6 corporate locations on New England Seacoast (Newburyport MA, Dover NH, Portsmouth NH, North Hampton NH, York ME, Rochester NH)","hq_city":"Newburyport","hq_state":"MA","lat":42.81,"lng":-70.87,"founded":1992,"status":"target","team":"Craig Annis (founder, 30+ years in fitness, UNH Whittemore School of Business grad); children Dailyn and Brady Annis have joined the business \u2014 second generation family legacy.","story":"Family-built 24-hour key club gym chain on the New England Seacoast. Craig Annis built the first location 30+ years ago, now has 6 corporate locations across NH, MA, and ME. Just launched franchising in spring 2026. The 'key club' model \u2014 members get 24/7 key access, no staff overhead, full equipment \u2014 is capital-light and proven. Second generation (Dailyn and Brady) are now involved, bringing digital marketing and modern operations. Membership model at $36/mo individual.","traction":"6 profitable corporate locations operating for 30+ years. Just launched franchising spring 2026 with $30K franchise fee, $200K-$525K total investment. Rochester NH is the newest location (pre-enrollment active). Strong local loyalty \u2014 members follow the brand across Seacoast.","funding":"Bootstrap / family-owned","entry_path":"Founding franchisee or master developer for new regions (outside New England Seacoast). The model is proven at 6 units across 3 states \u2014 ready for regional replication. Dan could also partner with the Annis family to accelerate franchise growth.","dan_value_add":"Franchise system buildout, multi-unit developer recruitment, brand strategy for national expansion, capital for franchise infrastructure","first_diligence":"Is the key club model proven outside the tight-knit Seacoast community? What's the unit-level profitability and member lifetime value? How does $36/mo pricing compare to Planet Fitness ($10) and boutique gyms?","sources":["https://www.vanguardkeyclubs.com/blog/family-legacy-drives-vkc","https://www.vanguardkeyclubs.com/franchise-ad-lp1","https://bostonvoyager.com/interview/meet-craig-annis-vanguard-key-clubs-northshore-newburyport-also-seacoast-new-hampshire-north-hampton-portsmouth-dover-york-maine/","https://1851franchise.com/building-vanguard-key-clubs-with-30-years-of-fitness-industry-expertise-2727450"],"buzz_signals":"30-year family legacy; second generation joining; just launched franchising spring 2026; local Seacoast loyalty","last_updated":"2026-07-19","added_date":"2026-07-19","source_file":"discovery_cron"},{"id":"sul-and-beans","name":"Sul & Beans","category":"Food & Beverage","subcategory":"Korean bingsoo / dessert cafe","units":6,"units_text":"~6 locations: Koreatown LA, Granada Hills CA, Irvine/Santa Clara CA, Frisco TX, Las Vegas NV","hq_city":"Los Angeles","hq_state":"CA","lat":34.06,"lng":-118.3,"founded":2014,"status":"watch","team":"Matt Kim (founder, also founded SomiSomi Soft Serve & Taiyaki in 2016). LinkedIn shows him as CEO of Sul & Beans since Feb 2014.","story":"Korean bingsoo (shaved ice dessert) cafe chain founded by Matt Kim in 2014 \u2014 predating his better-known SomiSomi brand. Sul & Beans brings authentic Korean bingsu to US markets. Strong in Korean-American communities (Koreatown LA, Santa Clara, Irvine) and expanding to Frisco TX and Las Vegas NV. The brand benefits from the broader Korean cultural wave (K-pop, K-dramas, K-beauty) driving interest in Korean food and desserts. Matt Kim is a proven multi-brand operator (SomiSomi has 33 locations).","traction":"~6 locations across CA, TX, NV. New Granada Hills location opened July 2026. Las Vegas location recently opened. Strong social media presence. High Yelp ratings (600+ reviews at multiple locations). Part of the Korean dessert trend alongside SomiSomi, Sulbing.","funding":"Bootstrap (founder-operated)","entry_path":"Dan could acquire or partner with Matt Kim on US expansion of Sul & Beans \u2014 Kim has proven franchise chops via SomiSomi. Alternatively, franchisee territory in new markets (Texas, Vegas, East Coast).","dan_value_add":"Multi-unit scaling capital, franchise system development (leveraging Kim's SomiSomi franchise experience), real estate strategy for Korean-American community markets","first_diligence":"Is Sul & Beans being actively grown or is it the secondary brand to SomiSomi? What's the unit-level revenue and profitability? Is Matt Kim willing to take on capital partners or is he committed to organic growth?","sources":["https://www.sulandbeans.com/","https://www.sulandbeans.com/contact","https://www.linkedin.com/in/jigeon-matt-kim-513030164","https://www.instagram.com/p/DaEbjc4mKU9/"],"buzz_signals":"Founder also created SomiSomi (33 locations); K-wave cultural tailwind; expanding to Texas and Las Vegas in 2026","last_updated":"2026-07-19","added_date":"2026-07-19","source_file":"discovery_cron"},{"id":"alexis-lauren-medspa","name":"ALEXIS LAUREN","category":"Med Spa & Wellness","subcategory":"Luxury medspa with membership model","units":2,"units_text":"2 locations in Miami area (Coral Gables, Bay Harbor Islands FL). Franchise launched Jan 2026.","hq_city":"Miami","hq_state":"FL","lat":25.72,"lng":-80.27,"founded":2022,"status":"watch","team":"Alexis Renda (founder & CEO). Female-founded brand. Building with a small team focused on personalized aesthetic treatments.","story":"Ultra-luxe medspa brand founded in 2022 by Alexis Renda in Miami. Differentiated by 'The Vault' membership model \u2014 turning client loyalty into predictable recurring revenue. Female-founded, positioning as a 'movement toward personalized aesthetic treatments' rather than just another injectables chain. Launched franchising January 2026 with $50K franchise fee and 6% royalties. Very early stage \u2014 only 2 corporate locations \u2014 but the membership model and luxury positioning are differentiated in a crowded medspa market.","traction":"2 corporate locations open (Coral Gables, Bay Harbor Islands). Launched franchise opportunity Jan 2026. Featured in Franchise Chatter, Skin Inc, and Athletech News. The Vault membership model drives recurring revenue. Miami market is a strong launchpad for luxury beauty brands.","funding":"Bootstrap / founder-funded","entry_path":"Founding franchisee in a new market, or partner with Alexis Renda to build out the franchise system. The brand is at the earliest possible stage for a franchise \u2014 2 units, just launched. High risk but high optionality.","dan_value_add":"Franchise system buildout, capital for franchise infrastructure, multi-unit developer recruitment, brand strategy for national luxury positioning","first_diligence":"Only 2 locations \u2014 is the concept proven beyond Miami's unique luxury market? What are the unit economics of the membership model (The Vault)? Is Alexis Renda committed to scaling or is this a lifestyle business?","sources":["https://alexislauren.com/","https://www.franchisechatter.com/2026/02/26/alexis-lauren-franchise-qa-with-alexis-renda-founder-and-ceo/","https://athletechnews.com/alexis-lauren-luxury-medspa-franchising/","https://www.medestheticsmag.com/home/article/22962951/alexis-lauren-medspa-franchise-membership-innovation"],"buzz_signals":"Female-founded luxury medspa; The Vault membership innovation; franchise launched Jan 2026; Franchise Times coverage","last_updated":"2026-07-19","added_date":"2026-07-19","source_file":"discovery_cron"}];

const CATEGORY_COLORS = {
'Youth Sports & Kids': '#7faa6f',
'Pet Services': '#d4825c',
'Auto Services': '#c9a050',
'Bakery': '#e8967d',
'Bagels': '#c9a850',
'Frozen Dessert': '#5b9ab8',
'Swedish Candy': '#d4565c',
'Fast Casual': '#e0a060',
'Beverage': '#6b8eb5',
'Med Spa & Wellness': '#c070a0',
'Beauty & Aesthetics': '#c070a0',
'Home Technology Services': '#7090c0',
'Consumer Services': '#999999',
};

let map, markerLayer, markers = {};
let activeCategory = null;

function init() {
map = L.map('map', { zoomControl: true, attributionControl: false }).setView([39.5, -98.35], 4);
L.tileLayer('https://{s}.basemaps.cartocdn.com/dark_nolabels/{z}/{x}/{y}{r}.png', {
maxZoom: 18, subdomains: 'abcd',
}).addTo(map);
L.tileLayer('https://{s}.basemaps.cartocdn.com/dark_only_labels/{z}/{x}/{y}{r}.png', {
maxZoom: 18, subdomains: 'abcd', pane: 'shadowPane'
}).addTo(map);
markerLayer = L.layerGroup().addTo(map);

const cats = [...new Set(TARGETS.map(t => t.category))].sort();
const sel = document.getElementById('categoryFilter');
cats.forEach(c => {
const opt = document.createElement('option');
opt.value = c; opt.textContent = c;
sel.appendChild(opt);
});
buildLegend();
applyFilters();
}

function buildLegend() {
const cats = [...new Set(TARGETS.map(t => t.category))].sort();
const legend = document.getElementById('legend');
let html = '<h4>Categories</h4>';
cats.forEach(c => {
const color = CATEGORY_COLORS[c] || '#999';
const count = TARGETS.filter(t => t.category === c).length;
html += '<div class="legend-item" onclick="toggleCategory(\'' + c + '\')">' +
'<div class="dot" style="background:' + color + '"></div>' +
'<span>' + c + '</span>' +
'<span class="count">' + count + '</span></div>';
});
legend.innerHTML = html;
}

function toggleCategory(cat) {
activeCategory = (activeCategory === cat) ? null : cat;
applyFilters();
}

function applyFilters() {
const search = document.getElementById('searchInput').value.toLowerCase();
const status = document.getElementById('statusFilter').value;
const category = document.getElementById('categoryFilter').value;
const unitFilter = document.getElementById('unitFilter').value;

const filtered = TARGETS.filter(t => {
if (search) {
const haystack = (t.name + ' ' + (t.hq_city||'') + ' ' + (t.story||'') + ' ' + (t.category||'')).toLowerCase();
if (!haystack.includes(search)) return false;
}
if (status && t.status !== status) return false;
const cat = category || activeCategory;
if (cat && t.category !== cat) return false;
if (unitFilter) {
const parts = unitFilter.split('-');
const min = parseInt(parts[0]); const max = parseInt(parts[1]);
const u = t.units || 0;
if (u < min || u > max) return false;
}
return true;
});
renderList(filtered);
renderMarkers(filtered);
renderStats(filtered);
}

function renderList(items) {
const list = document.getElementById('targetList');
document.getElementById('totalCount').textContent = items.length;
if (items.length === 0) {
list.innerHTML = '<div class="empty-state">No targets match filters.<br>Try widening your search.</div>';
return;
}
list.innerHTML = items.map(t => {
const color = CATEGORY_COLORS[t.category] || '#999';
return '<div class="list-item" onclick="selectTarget(\'' + t.id + '\')" data-id="' + t.id + '">' +
'<div class="list-item-dot" style="background:' + color + '"></div>' +
'<div class="list-item-content">' +
'<div class="list-item-name">' + t.name + '</div>' +
'<div class="list-item-meta">' +
'<span class="units">' + (t.units || '?') + ' units</span>' +
'<span>' + (t.hq_city || '') + (t.hq_state ? ', ' + t.hq_state : '') + '</span>' +
'<span class="badge b-' + t.status + '">' + t.status + '</span>' +
'</div>' +
'<div class="list-item-meta" style="margin-top:2px;font-size:10px">' + t.category + '</div>' +
'</div></div>';
}).join('');
}

function renderMarkers(items) {
markerLayer.clearLayers();
markers = {};
items.forEach(t => {
if (!t.lat || !t.lng) return;
const color = CATEGORY_COLORS[t.category] || '#999';
const marker = L.circleMarker([t.lat, t.lng], {
radius: 8, fillColor: color, color: '#0a0d12',
weight: 2, opacity: 1, fillOpacity: 0.85
});
const statusIcon = {target:'Target', watch:'Watch', comp:'Comp', kill:'Kill'}[t.status] || '';
marker.bindPopup(
'<b>' + t.name + '</b>' +
'<div class="popup-meta">' + statusIcon + ' &middot; ' + (t.units || '?') + ' units &middot; ' + t.category + '</div>' +
'<div class="popup-meta">' + (t.hq_city || '') + (t.hq_state ? ', ' + t.hq_state : '') + '</div>' +
'<div style="margin-top:8px"><a href="#" onclick="selectTarget(\'' + t.id + '\'); return false;">View details &rarr;</a></div>',
{maxWidth: 260}
);
marker.on('click', function() { selectTarget(t.id, false); });
marker.addTo(markerLayer);
markers[t.id] = marker;
});
}

function renderStats(items) {
const targets = items.filter(t => t.status === 'target').length;
const watch = items.filter(t => t.status === 'watch').length;
const comp = items.filter(t => t.status === 'comp').length;
const geocoded = items.filter(t => t.lat && t.lng).length;
document.getElementById('statsBar').innerHTML =
'<span><b>' + targets + '</b> targets</span>' +
'<span><b>' + watch + '</b> watch</span>' +
'<span><b>' + comp + '</b> comp</span>' +
'<span><b>' + geocoded + '</b> mapped</span>';
}

function selectTarget(id, fly) {
if (fly === undefined) fly = true;
const t = TARGETS.find(function(x) { return x.id === id; });
if (!t) return;
document.querySelectorAll('.list-item').forEach(function(el) { el.classList.remove('active'); });
const li = document.querySelector('[data-id="' + id + '"]');
if (li) { li.classList.add('active'); li.scrollIntoView({block:'nearest'}); }
if (fly && markers[id]) {
map.flyTo([t.lat, t.lng], 7, {duration: 0.8});
setTimeout(function() { if (markers[id]) markers[id].openPopup(); }, 600);
}
const color = CATEGORY_COLORS[t.category] || '#999';
const statusBadge = '<span class="badge b-' + t.status + '">' + t.status.toUpperCase() + '</span>';
const sources = (t.sources || []).map(function(s) {
let label = s;
try { label = new URL(s).hostname.replace('www.',''); } catch(e) {}
return '<a href="' + s + '" target="_blank">' + label + '</a>';
}).join('');
const buzzList = (t.buzz_signals || []).filter(function(b) { return b; }).map(function(b) {
return '<li>' + b + '</li>';
}).join('');

document.getElementById('detailContent').innerHTML =
'<span class="kicker" style="color:' + color + ';border-color:' + color + '33;background:' + color + '11">' + t.category + (t.subcategory ? ' &middot; ' + t.subcategory : '') + '</span>' +
'<h2>' + t.name + '</h2>' +
'<div class="sub">' + statusBadge + ' ' + (t.units || '?') + ' units &middot; ' + (t.hq_city || '') + (t.hq_state ? ', ' + t.hq_state : '') + (t.founded ? ' &middot; Founded ' + t.founded : '') + '</div>' +
'<div class="meta-grid">' +
'<div class="meta-item"><label>Units</label><span>' + (t.units_text || t.units || '\u2014') + '</span></div>' +
'<div class="meta-item"><label>Funding</label><span>' + (t.funding || 'Bootstrap') + '</span></div>' +
'<div class="meta-item"><label>Entry Path</label><span>' + (t.entry_path ? t.entry_path.substring(0,60) : '\u2014') + '</span></div>' +
'<div class="meta-item"><label>Status</label><span style="text-transform:capitalize">' + t.status + '</span></div>' +
'</div>' +
(t.story ? '<h3>Story</h3><div class="field-box"><p>' + t.story + '</p></div>' : '') +
(t.traction ? '<h3>Traction</h3><div class="field-box gold"><p>' + t.traction + '</p></div>' : '') +
(t.team ? '<h3>Team</h3><div class="field-box"><p>' + t.team + '</p></div>' : '') +
(buzzList ? '<h3>Buzz Signals</h3><div class="field-box green"><ul style="margin:0;padding-left:18px">' + buzzList + '</ul></div>' : '') +
(t.dan_value_add ? '<h3>Dan\'s Value Add</h3><div class="field-box blue"><p>' + t.dan_value_add + '</p></div>' : '') +
(t.first_diligence ? '<h3>First Diligence Question</h3><div class="field-box clay"><p>' + t.first_diligence + '</p></div>' : '') +
(sources ? '<div class="sources">' + sources + '</div>' : '') +
'<div style="margin-top:20px;font-size:10px;color:var(--muted)">Added: ' + (t.added_date || '?') + ' &middot; Updated: ' + (t.last_updated || '?') + '</div>';

document.getElementById('detailPanel').classList.add('open');
}

function closeDetail() {
document.getElementById('detailPanel').classList.remove('open');
document.querySelectorAll('.list-item').forEach(function(el) { el.classList.remove('active'); });
}

document.addEventListener('keydown', function(e) { if (e.key === 'Escape') closeDetail(); });
init();
</script>
</body>
